      *              * numero di records caricati oppure no            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008    >    w-rlt-sup-max
                     go to vis-cor-reg-300
           else      go to vis-cor-reg-400.
       vis-cor-reg-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
