      *              * ricati                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione linea a Spaces              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "B"                  to   w-cnt-cor-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008    to   w-cnt-cor-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-cor-000      thru vis-lin-cor-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Continuazione                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-cor-reg-500.
       vis-cor-reg-400.
